| `fable-dev-conversations` | `PK` (USER#userId) | `SK` (CONV#convId) | Chat history |

#### Builds Table Schema

```typescript
interface Build {
  PK: string;              // ORG#<orgId>
  SK: string;              // BUILD#<buildId>
  buildId: string;
  request: string;
  spec: object;
  status: 'pending' | 'running' | 'completed' | 'failed';
  userId: string;
  orgId: string;
  conversationId?: string;
  result?: object;
  createdAt: string;
  updatedAt: string;
}
```

